%20and%20her%20husband%20spent%20%2455%2C000%20over%20the%20past%20year%20to%20make%20their%20Kansas%20City-area%20home%20more%20appealing%20for%20short-term%20renters.%20The%20four-bedroom%20home%20features%20the%20kind%20of%20touches%20%E2%80%94%20cozy%20TV-watching%20areas%2C%20an%20outdoor%20fire%20pit%2C%20and%20newly%20purchased%20furniture%20%E2%80%94%20that%20should%20be%20catnip%20for%20visitors.%20Since%20the%20listing%20went%20live%20in%20December%2C%20however%2C%20the%20home%20has%20drawn%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20bookings.%20The%20first%20stay%20didn't%20offer%20much%20encouragement%3A%20the%20guests%20trashed%20the%20place%2C%20causing%20about%20%241%2C200%20in%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20a%20baptism%20by%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Totta%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20high%20hopes%20for%20this%20summer%2C%20though%2C%20when%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffifa-2026-world-cup-ticket-prices-expensive-usa-canada-mexico-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeliver%20tens%20of%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esoccer%20fans%20to%20their%20backyard.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-2026-cities-arenas-hosting-games-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKansas%20City's%20selection%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20one%20of%2016%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENorth%20American%20host%20cities%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20decided%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20rental%20game%20%E2%80%94%20Totta%20says%20she%20was%20intrigued%20after%20hearing%20about%20a%20friend's%20plans%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20influx%20of%20out-of-towners.%20With%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanning-vacation-nightmare-then-came-ai-plane-pricing-airbnb-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20of%20dynamic-pricing%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20advises%20her%20on%20daily%20rates%20(for%20which%20she%20only%20pays%20%2420%20a%20month)%2C%20Totta%20has%20set%20a%20goal%20of%20earning%20at%20least%20%242%2C500%20per%20night%20during%20the%20festivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20a%20banner%20year%20for%20rental%20owners%20who%2C%20like%20Totta%2C%20own%20properties%20near%20some%20of%20the%20country's%20biggest%20sports%20stadiums.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftickets%2Fsuper-bowl-tickets-seahawks-vs-patriots-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Super%20Bowl%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20there's%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20put%20a%20roof%20over%20the%20heads%20of%20a%20couple%20(or%20couple%20dozen)%20fans%20who%20need%20a%20place%20to%20crash.%20Airbnb%20hosts%20in%20places%20like%20Dallas%2C%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20are%20expected%20to%20rake%20in%20%24212%20million%20from%20the%20World%20Cup%20alone%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20Deloitte%20(those%20estimates%20don't%20include%20earnings%20on%20other%20short-term%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvrbo-said-it-will-stop-ads-poking-fun-at-airbnb-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erental%20platforms%20like%20Vrbo%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Some%20operators%20aim%20to%20bank%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20per%20night.%20In%20Kansas%20City%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20median%20asking%20rates%20for%20short-term%20rentals%20on%20the%20night%20of%20June%2016%2C%20when%20Algeria%20and%20Argentina%20face%20off%20in%20the%20tournament's%20group%20stage%2C%20are%20up%20more%20than%20200%25%20from%20a%20year%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20of%20rental%20riches%20is%20drawing%20everyone%20from%20veteran%20property%20managers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-of-new-airbnb-hosts-locations-profits-challenges-advice-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewbies%20eager%20for%20a%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20action.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20it's%20never%20been%20easier%20to%20try%20your%20hand%20at%20short-term%20rentals.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-and-pop-landlords-homeownership-rent-wall-street-corporate-investors-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esqueeze%20every%20last%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20of%20your%20home%2C%20a%20vast%20array%20of%20software%20providers%20can%20advise%20you%20on%20pricing%20and%20listing%20strategies.%20If%20ease%20is%20what%20you're%20after%2C%20on-the-ground%20management%20companies%20stand%20ready%20to%20handle%20every%20last%20headache%20(for%20a%20fee%2C%20of%20course).%20But%20while%20fans%20are%20willing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-vacation-rental-home-boom-airbnb-hotels-wealthy-travelers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esplurge%20on%20top-tier%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20prime%20locations%2C%20some%20of%20these%20wannabe%20landlords%20are%20destined%20for%20letdowns.%20The%20days%20of%20snapping%20a%20few%20iPhone%20photos%20and%20tossing%20a%20home%20on%20Airbnb%20with%20a%20premium%20price%20tag%20are%20over.%20To%20stand%20out%20from%20their%20ever-savvier%20competition%2C%20homeowners%20are%20decking%20out%20their%20places%20in%20decor%20tailored%20to%20the%20most%20diehard%20fans%20and%20providing%20the%20kinds%20of%20flourishes%2C%20like%20freshly%20made%20treats%20or%20luxury%20linens%2C%20that%20are%20typically%20associated%20with%20five-star%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProximity%20to%20the%20stadium%20is%20nice.%20In%20the%20cutthroat%20world%20of%20sports%20houses%2C%20though%2C%20that's%20just%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20size%20of%20the%20sports%20tourism%20market%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-book-airbnbs-instead-of-hotels-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20popularity%20of%20non-hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20options%20for%20these%20weary%20travelers%2C%20has%20made%20the%20short-term%20rental%20business%20a%20natural%20temptation%20for%20anyone%20within%20spitting%20distance%20of%20an%20arena.%20Sports%20fans%20around%20the%20country%20spent%20a%20whopping%20%246.9%20billion%20on%20lodging%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20annual%20report%20from%20the%20Sports%20Events%20and%20Tourism%20Association.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20Oxford%20Economics%20found%20that%20short-term%20rentals%20saw%20a%20larger%20increase%20in%20demand%20than%20hotels%20and%20cruises%20combined.%20The%20desire%20for%20beds%20near%20major%20sporting%20events%20has%20spawned%20a%20cottage%20industry%20of%20homeowners%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-make-30000-a-year-airbnb-host-side-gig%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoonlight%20as%20landlords%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year%2C%20investors%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-host-how-to-select-a-short-term-rental-property-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20properties%20to%20rent%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20to%20cash-flush%20fans%2C%20and%20management%20companies%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frental-vacation-property-manager-career-journey-lessons-advice-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshoulder%20the%20hassle%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20running%20mini-hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERent%20Like%20A%20Champion%2C%20founded%20in%202006%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eby%20a%20couple%20of%20Notre%20Dame%20alums%2C%20started%20out%20managing%20short-term%20rentals%20for%20college-town%20homeowners%20looking%20to%20make%20some%20extra%20money%20on%20busy%20football%20weekends.%20The%20company%20now%20also%20partners%20with%20event%20organizers%20like%20the%20PGA%20of%20America%20to%20secure%20accommodations%20for%20fans%2C%20corporate%20clients%2C%20and%20athletes.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20its%20hosts%20are%20regular%20homeowners%20rather%20than%20full-time%20real%20estate%20investors%2C%20says%20CEO%20Dave%20Longwell%2C%20and%20the%20most%20sought-after%20listings%20can%20earn%20five%20figures%20for%20a%20weeklong%20event.%20But%20he%20cautions%20that%20the%20eye-catching%20paydays%20are%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%2010%2C%2020%20miles%20from%20the%20event%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20quality%20renter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20customers%20are%20savvy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experiences%20of%20these%20part-time%20hosts%20could%20offer%20a%20road%20map%20for%20those%20hoping%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20World%20Cup%20gold%20rush.%20Lisa%20Hinkle%2C%20a%2063-year-old%20client%20of%20Rent%20Like%20A%20Champion%20who%20lives%20walking%20distance%20from%20Notre%20Dame's%20football%20stadium%20in%20South%20Bend%2C%20Indiana%2C%20says%20two-night%20stays%20for%20games%20can%20bring%20in%20anywhere%20from%20%243%2C500%20to%20%243%2C800%2C%20while%20the%20biggest%20home%20game%20of%20the%20season%20%E2%80%94%20likely%20the%20Fighting%20Irish's%20matchup%20against%20national%20title%20runner-up%20Miami%20this%20coming%20fall%20%E2%80%94%20could%20reach%20%245%2C000.%20Those%20windfalls%20don't%20come%20easy%2C%20though.%20Hinkle%2C%20who%20works%20two%20jobs%2C%20says%20she%20spends%20about%2010%20to%2020%20hours%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-airbnb-cleaning-fee-less-bookings-not-dipping-into-profit-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20and%20preparing%20the%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20next%20guests%20after%20a%20stay.%20She's%20carried%20out%20various%20remodels%20over%20the%20years%2C%20from%20upgrading%20bathrooms%20to%20adding%20more%20beds%20so%20the%20house%20can%20sleep%20up%20to%2016%20people.%20She%20pays%20a%20friend%20to%20help%20with%20the%20cleaning%2C%20while%20Rent%20Like%20A%20Champion%20takes%20a%2015%25%20cut%20of%20her%20revenue%20in%20exchange%20for%20finding%2C%20vetting%2C%20and%20insuring%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20money%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Hinkle%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20flair%20doesn't%20hurt%2C%20either.%20Hinkle%20outfits%20the%20house%20with%20Notre%20Dame-branded%20towels%2C%20mugs%2C%20and%20other%20decor%2C%20including%20Fighting%20Irish-themed%20cornhole%20and%20an%20inflatable%20leprechaun%20outside%20on%20game%20weekends.%20She%20leaves%20pastries%20from%20a%20local%20baker%20and%20personally%20checks%20in%20with%20guests%2C%20offering%20flexibility%20for%20check-in%20or%20check-out%20times%20if%20needed.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20appreciate%20the%20extra%20little%20added%20touches%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brightly%20colored%20rental%20homes%20in%20pink%2C%20sea%20foam%20green%2C%20and%20yellow%2C%20with%20Lucas%20Oil%20Stadium%20in%20Indianapolis%2C%20Indiana%2C%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69822ba0a645d11881888fd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJD%20Holly%20purchased%20these%20three%20eye-catching%20rental%20homes%20in%20Indianapolis%2C%20Indiana%2C%20roughly%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20long%20before%20construction%20on%20Lucas%20Oil%20Stadium%20wrapped%20up%20in%202008.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20JD%20Holly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Indianapolis%2C%20JD%20Holly%20combines%20marketing%20savvy%20with%20the%20old%20real%20estate%20adage%20of%20%26quot%3Blocation%2C%20location%2C%20location.%26quot%3B%20He%20owns%20a%20few%20rental%20homes%20about%20a%20five-minute%20walk%20from%20Lucas%20Oil%20Stadium%2C%20home%20to%20the%20NFL's%20Indianapolis%20Colts%20and%20a%20bevy%20of%20big-time%20events%20like%20gaming%20conventions%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20concerts.%20In%20landlocked%2C%20sports-crazed%20Indianapolis%2C%20that%20proximity%20is%20as%20good%20as%20%26quot%3Bbeachfront%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Holly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crown%20jewel%20of%20the%20bunch%20is%20a%20custom-built%2C%20two-story%20home%20made%20out%20of%20shipping%20containers%20and%20decked%20out%20in%20the%20Colts'%20blue%20and%20white%2C%20with%20the%20team's%20logo%20painted%20above%20the%20entrance.%20There's%20ample%20space%20for%20tailgating%20outside%2C%20while%20the%20interior%20boasts%20seven%20TVs%2C%20a%20bar%2C%20and%20accommodations%20for%20eight%20people.%20During%20big-game%20weekends%2C%20the%20place%20rents%20for%20as%20much%20as%20%241%2C500%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20pretty%20much%20shocked%20that%20I'm%20doing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Holly%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20I%20never%20in%20my%20life%20thought%20I'd%20be%20in%20the%20short-term%20rental%2C%20hospitality%20business%2C%20but%20it's%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Short-Term%20Rental%20Alliance%20and%20Missouri%20Vacation%20Home%20Alliance%20hosted%20a%20crash%20course%20for%20homeowners%20interested%20in%20listing%20their%20properties%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Tyann%20Marcink%20Hammond%2C%20owner%20of%20the%20vacation%20rental%20company%20Branson%20Family%20Retreats%20and%20%26quot%3BQueen%20of%20Guest%20Experience%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20she's%20known%20around%20the%20industry%2C%20says%20her%20message%20to%20potential%20landlords%20was%20to%20shed%20any%20social%20media-induced%20fantasies%20of%20handing%20off%20the%20keys%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Byou%20go%20sit%20on%20a%20beach%20with%20an%20umbrella%20drink%20in%20your%20hand.%26quot%3B%20Seemingly%20simple%20choices%2C%20like%20the%20kinds%20of%20towels%20or%20linens%20on%20offer%2C%20or%20how%20guests%20will%20even%20get%20%3Cem%3Einside%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20house%2C%20can%20give%20rise%20to%20sprawling%20decision%20trees%20that%20can%20stump%20any%20host.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20November%20session%20%E2%80%94%20another%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Feb.%206%20and%207%20%E2%80%94%20attendees%20weren't%20as%20concerned%20with%20those%20minute%20details.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20most%20interested%20in%20learning%20about%20pricing.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20know%2C%20is%20it%20worth%20their%20time%20and%20energy%3F%26quot%3B%20Marcink%20Hammond%20tells%20me.%20They%20may%20also%20be%20wondering%20exactly%20how%20much%20they%20stand%20to%20net%20when%20the%20dust%20settles.%20Examples%20of%20outlandish%20paydays%20abound%3A%20If%20they%20somehow%20haven't%20caught%20the%20hubbub%20around%20%245%2C000-a-night%20listings%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20then%20maybe%20they've%20heard%20about%20the%20small-town%20Georgia%20residents%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-tournament-week-north-augusta-sc-home-rental-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearn%20a%20year's%20worth%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20mortgage%20payments%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-billionaires-favorite-golf-tournament-kicks-off-augusta-national-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMasters%20Tournament%20descends%20upon%20Augusta%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20help%20homeowners%20wring%20every%20last%20dollar%20out%20of%20their%20short-term%20rentals%2C%20tech%20companies%20like%20PriceLabs%2C%20Eviivo%2C%20and%20AirDNA%20offer%20relatively%20cheap%20tools%20that%20replace%20guesswork%20with%20science.%20The%20abundance%20of%20insights%2C%20however%2C%20can't%20replace%20the%20grunt%20work%20of%20old-fashioned%20hospitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20can%20communicate%20that%20you%20know%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Marcink%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20higher%20rate%20that%20you%20can%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHosts%20seeking%20top%20dollar%20don't%20have%20long%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20join%20the%20fray%20or%20sit%20this%20one%20out.%20Jamie%20Lane%2C%20AirDNA's%20chief%20economist%2C%20says%20the%20company%20has%20seen%20strong%20booking%20demand%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20Vrbo%2C%20where%20Kansas%20City%20is%20already%20more%20than%2040%25%20occupied%20for%20the%20tournament's%20group%20stage.%20Lane%20says%20he%20expects%20to%20see%20a%20pop%20of%20supply%20a%20little%20closer%20to%20the%20event%2C%20as%20more%20people%20catch%20word%20of%20the%20rates%20their%20neighbors%20are%20getting.%20But%20waiting%20too%20long%20could%20be%20a%20losing%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELane%20compared%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20experience%20of%20hosts%20in%20Paris%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-olympics-awful-surprises-reporter-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprior%20to%20the%202024%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Paris%20saw%20a%2050%25%20jump%20in%20inventory%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20Vrbo%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20astonishing%26quot%3B%20increase%2C%20Lane%20says%2C%20given%20that%20the%20city%20is%20already%20Airbnb's%20second-largest%20market%20in%20the%20world.%20Most%20of%20those%20new%20listings%20came%20in%20about%20three%20or%20four%20months%20before%20the%20event%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20enough%20time%20to%20build%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20reputation%20on%20the%20platform.%20Sophisticated%20travelers%20gravitate%20toward%20experienced%20hosts%20and%20places%20with%20a%20track%20record%20of%20good%20reviews%2C%20Lane%20says%2C%20and%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20gamble%20on%20a%20new%20listing.%20If%20potential%20World%20Cup%20landlords%20want%20to%20get%20a%20good%20rate%20when%20things%20kick%20off%20in%20June%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20get%20some%20reps%20in%20this%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMyriam%20Totta%2C%20the%20Kansas%20City-area%20host%2C%20hopes%20to%20reap%20the%20rewards%20of%20solid%20planning.%20She%20has%20some%20bookings%20lined%20up%20for%