years%20of%20testing%20sleep%20products.%20Each%20morning%2C%20I%20would%20record%20any%20soreness%20I%20felt%20and%20how%20comfortable%20the%20topper%20felt%20the%20previous%20night.%20I'd%20then%20look%20at%20my%20sleep%20stats%20collected%20using%20my%20smart%20watch%20and%20note%20which%20positions%20felt%20most%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20isolation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20placed%20my%20phone%20with%20a%20vibrometer%20app%20open%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20about%2012%20inches%20from%20the%20right%20side.%20Next%2C%20I%20lifted%20a%2015-pound%20bowling%20ball%20above%20my%20head%20and%20dropped%20it%20onto%20the%20topper%20so%20that%20it%20landed%20about%2012%20inches%20from%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20(and%2036%20inches%20from%20the%20phone).%20I%20performed%20this%20test%20five%20times%20and%20kept%20the%20median%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20and%20warranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIdeally%2C%20you%20can%20return%20a%20topper%20if%20it's%20not%20suitable%20for%20your%20body%20type%20and%20sleeping%20style.%20I%20looked%20at%20each%20topper's%20return%20policy%2Ftrial%20period%20and%20looked%20for%20any%20loopholes%2C%20like%20shipping%20costs.%20The%20median%20trial%20period%20for%20the%20models%20we%20tested%20was%2030%20nights%2C%20and%20I%20docked%20points%20if%20a%20topper%20didn't%20have%20a%20trial%20period.%20Also%2C%20since%20you%20want%20your%20topper%20to%20last%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20the%20warranties.%20The%20median%20warranty%20length%20is%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d76e5b38-0bed-416a-8b57-30785110fb57%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20mattress%20toppers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rolled%20up%20mattress%20topper%20is%20on%20a%20bare%20mattress%20as%20part%20of%20testing%20for%20the%20best%20mattress%20topper.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd414a41237