lience%2C%20showed%20promising%20results%20in%20increasing%20essential%20nutrient%20levels%20by%20up%20to%2080%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20introducing%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20enrich%20the%20soil%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20seeds%20enabled%20plants%20to%20absorb%20more%20nutrients%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20significantly%20higher%20nutritional%20content%20in%20the%20harvested%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20baseline%20levels%20of%20zinc%20in%20the%20traditional%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20around%2028%20parts%20per%20million%20whereas%2C%20it%20is%2045%20parts%20per%20million%20in%20the%20newer%20bio%20fortified%20seeds.%20We%20also%20add%20a%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20the%20soil%20which%20helps%20mobilise%20the%20naturally%20available%20zinc%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20roots.%20This%20increases%20zinc%20base%20levels%20to%2050-55%20parts%20per%20million%20%E2%80%93%20an%20increment%20of%20about%2080%20percent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20every%20seed%20will%20have%20its%20own%20benefits%20and%20drawbacks.%20These%20seeds%20give%20almost%2080%20percent%20more%20nutritional%20value%20but%20farmers%20may%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20of%204%20to%205%20percent%20in%20yield.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349986%2Fprabhat-kumar-sumarth-ngo-bihar-horticulture-training-for-farmers-double-income-cash-crops%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremium%20rates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20such%20produce%20covers%20up%20the%20yield%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborations%20with%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20across%20regions%20like%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Basti%2C%20Gonda%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20and%20others%2C%20the%20initiative%20not%20only%20promoted%20the%20adoption%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20but%20also%20provided%20holistic%20services%20ranging%20from%20soil%20analysis%20to%20crop%20selection%20in%20order%20to%20boost%20crop%20nutrient%20content%20naturally.%20Greenday%20has%20achieved%20an%20annual%C2%A0turnover%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20impact%20created%20by%20their%20startup%2C%20Aishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20spending%202.5%20years%20in%20Sitapur%20closely%20working%20with%20farmers%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%20in%20something%20as%20small%20as%20a%20seed.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20massive%20impact%20by%20working%20for%20our%20farmers.%20Seeing%20their%20dedication%20first%20hand%20has%20been%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experience.%20Their%20hard%20work%20fuels%20our%20passion%20to%20turn%20our%20brand%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20improves%20health%20but%20also%20supports%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20All%20photos%3A%20Greenday.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757059200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496772%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow-based%20Aishwarya%20Bhatnagar%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%20run%20Greenday%20to%20promote%20innovative%20farming%20methods%20and%20biofortified%20seeds%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496772%2Fgreenday-biofortified-seeds-lucknow-farmer-income-nutrition%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20%E2%80%98Sadya%E2%80%99%20Feast%3A%20Onam%20Festival%20Traditions%2C%20Dances%20%26amp%3B%20Boat%20Races%20You%20Must%20See%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnam%20is%20often%20celebrated%20through%20its%20grandest%20highlight%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Onam%20%3Cem%3ESadya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20lavish%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F491736%2Fonam-2025-kerala-sadhya-authentic-recipes-by-top-chefs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetarian%20feast%20served%20on%20banana%20leaves%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20enjoyed%20with%20family%20and%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20the%20kitchens%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3ESadya%3C%2Fem%3E%20takes%20centre%20stage%20lies%20an%20equally%20vibrant%20world%20of%20rituals%2C%20performances%2C%20and%20traditions.%20From%20%3Cem%3EPulikali%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3Etiger%20dance%20and%20%3Cem%3EKummatti%20Kali%E2%80%